AFTER A DR. SHELDON WALLACE,

00:44.208 --> 00:46.166
FROM YOUR PRACTICE,
SPOKE TO LEE McHENRY,

00:46.208 --> 00:48.250
SO THAT'S ALSO TAINTED.

00:48.291 --> 00:50.250
AND, MS. KING,
I MEAN NO DISRESPECT,

00:50.291 --> 00:53.000
BUT YOU'RE A SEX THERAPIST WITH
A HISTORY OF MEETING STRANGE MEN

00:53.041 --> 00:55.500
