AT BEST BE DESCRIBED

00:55.542 --> 00:57.500
AS FETISHISTIC
SEXUAL ENCOUNTERS.

00:57.542 --> 01:00.041
I KNOW THE CASE.

01:00.083 --> 01:03.291
MR. FREEDMAN, I GRADUATED FIRST
IN MY CLASS FROM STANFORD.

01:03.333 --> 01:05.542
I HAVE A 90% CONVICTION RATE
HERE IN THE D.A.'s OFFICE,

01:05.583 --> 01:07.583
100% ON RAPE,
SO I'M PRETTY DAMN GOOD,

01:07.625 --> 01:10.000
WHICH IS WHY I CAN SAY TO YOU
WITHOUT HESITATION

01:10.041 --> 01:13.000
THAT THERE IS NO WAY THIS OFFICE
IS GOING TO CHARGE LEE McHENRY.

01:13.041 --> 01:15.542
I'M SORRY.

01:20.959 --> 01:22.500
HAVE A NICE DAY.

01:41.500 --> 01:43.542
(Naomi) THIS IS
THE RIBBON CUTTING CEREMONY

01:43.583 --> 01:46.417
OF THE NEW HOSPITAL
IN WESTERN INDIA.

01:46.458 --> 01:48.875
THIS WAS ALSO THE DAY
THAT OLIVIA SAT UP ON HER OWN

01:48.917 --> 01:51.458
FOR THE FIRST TIME.
MAYA AND I SKYPED.
THAT'S INCREDIBLE.

01:51.500 --> 01:53.625
THAT'S
QUITE AN ACCOMPLISHMENT.

01:53.667 --> 01:55.500
THE HOSPITAL, I MEAN.
BUT OLIVIA'S GREAT, TOO.

01:55.542 --> 01:58.083
YEAH. (laughs) AND HERE,
THE FOUNDATION IS DELIVERING

01:58.125 --> 02:01.458
A BOATLOAD
OF MOSQUITO NETS TO TANZANIA.
WOW.

02:01.500 --> 02:03.750
BOATLOAD. IT'S AN ACTUAL BOAT
LOADED WITH MOSQUITO NETS.

02:03.792 --> 02:05.625
THAT'S SO COOL.
(laughs)

02:05.667 --> 02:08.709
ACTUALLY, THAT'S WHERE I WAS
WHEN I FOUND OUT ABOUT,

02:08.750 --> 02:11.041
UH, BETSEY'S AUNT
ABANDONING HER.

02:11.083 --> 02:13.125
UM...

02:13.166 --> 02:15.959
THIS IS LAOS, AND HERE,
WE WERE ABLE TO DELIVER

02:16.000 --> 02:18.667
ENOUGH VACCINE
TO IMMUNIZE 2,000 CHILDREN.

02:18.709 --> 02:19.917
WOW.

02:19.959 --> 02:21.917
YEAH, AND THAT'S WHERE I WAS

02:21.959 --> 02:24.583
WHEN I FOUND OUT
ABOUT CHARLOTTE.

02:24.625 --> 02:26.667
YEAH, A LOT...

02:26.709 --> 02:29.000
HAS HAPPENED
SINCE YOU'VE BEEN GONE.

02:31.792 --> 02:33.375
UH, OH.

02:33.417 --> 02:35.125
I HAVE A PATIENT.

02:35.166 --> 02:37.125
IT WAS GREAT
TO SEE YOU, NAI.

02:37.166 --> 02:40.166
YEAH.
ALL RIGHT.

02:40.208 --> 02:42.208
WHAT WAS THAT?

02:42.250 --> 02:44.041
NOTHING.
YOU LOOK AMAZING.

02:44.083 --> 02:45.750
I MEAN, FOR SOMEONE...
(Violet) YOU DO.

02:45.792 --> 02:47.542
WHO'S TREKKED ACROSS
THREE CONTINENTS...

02:47.583 --> 02:49.542
(laughs)
OH, YOU KNOW, I JUST--

02:49.583 --> 02:51.542
I'M ALL "EAT PRAY LOVE,"
YOU KNOW?

02:51.583 --> 02:53.917
I'M--I'M, UH, VERY ZEN.
ZEN?

02:53.959 --> 02:55.834
DOES THAT MEAN
YOU'RE NOW ALL RIGHT

02:55.875 --> 02:57.834
WITH ADDISON SLEEPING
WITH YOUR EX-HUSBAND?
AMELIA!

02:57.875 --> 02:59.959
(Violet) FILTER.
SORRY. I'M WORKING ON IT.

03:00.000 --> 03:03.917
WELL, I FOR ONE AM GLAD
TO HAVE YOU BACK, SO...
THANK YOU.

03:03.959 --> 03:06.500
ALL RIGHT, TRUTH--
HOW IS CHARLOTTE?

03:06.542 --> 03:08.667
RAPE-Y AND WEIRD.

03:08.709 --> 03:10.542
(sighs) FILTER.

03:10.583 --> 03:13.041
CHARLOTTE... IS DOING
THE BEST SHE CAN.

03:13.083 --> 03:15.041
(Pete) HEY.

03:15.083 --> 03:17.041
EMILY WENDAL
IS BACK IN THE E.R.

03:17.083 --> 03:18.750
DAMN IT.

03:18.792 --> 03:19.834
AGAIN?

03:19.875 --> 03:22.834
WHAT,
WHO IS EMILY WENDAL?

03:22.875 --> 03:24.959
YOU SHOULD COME, TOO.

03:25.000 --> 03:28.041
HEY, UM... THE GUYS
ARE PLAYING POKER TONIGHT.

03:28.083 --> 03:30.583
YOU WANT TO DO A GIRLS' NIGHT,
GET ALL OF US TOGETHER,

03:30.625 --> 03:32.333
CATCH UP?
UH, YEAH, YEAH, I'M IN.

03:32.375 --> 03:34.041
YEAH?
YEAH.

03:34.083 --> 03:37.458
I'M GLAD YOU'RE BACK.

03:37.500 --> 03:40.792
I MISSED YOU.

03:40.834 --> 03:43.667
ARE YOU OKAY
WITH HER SCREWING SAM?

03:43.709 --> 03:45.166
FILTER.
YEAH.

03:45.208 --> 03:47.709
