OKAY.

03:51.083 --> 03:52.875
(blows air, clicks gearshift)

03:52.917 --> 03:56.041
I DON'T KNOW. I'M GONNA TRY
TO MAKE SOME PHONE CALLS,

03:56.083 --> 03:58.625
SEE IF THERE'S ANYTHING
I CAN...

03:58.667 --> 04:01.041
HOW DO THEY
NOT CHARGE THE BASTARD?

04:01.083 --> 04:04.500
WHAT WILL BE WILL BE.

04:04.542 --> 04:06.875
CHARLOTTE...

04:06.917 --> 04:08.875
YOU SEEM FINE.

04:08.917 --> 04:11.625
ARE YOU...
ARE YOU OKAY WITH THIS,

04:11.667 --> 04:14.208
WITH THEM
LETTING THAT GUY WALK?

04:14.250 --> 04:15.834
I'M RIGHT AS RAIN.

04:15.875 --> 04:17.333
OKAY. GOOD.

04:17.375 --> 04:19.333
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
THAT YOU FEEL

04:19.375 --> 04:21.333
LIKE YOU'RE IN CONTROL
OF WHAT HAPPENS.

04:21.375 --> 04:23.041
THIS IS YOUR CASE.

04:23.083 --> 04:25.625
YOU KNOW, YOU HAVE
THE RIGHT TO FEEL SAFE.

04:25.667 --> 04:28.875
I'M IN THE DRIVER'S SEAT NOW.
OF COURSE YOU ARE.

04:28.917 --> 04:30.875
AND I KNOW
RECOVERY IS A PROCESS,

04:30.917 --> 04:33.041
SO IT'S OKAY
IF YOU'RE NOT FINE.

04:33.083 --> 04:36.041
BUT WE WILL GET THROUGH IT,
TOGETHER.

04:36.083 --> 04:39.333
YOU KNOW, IT'S A MARATHON,
NOT A SPRINT.

04:39.375 --> 04:40.917
RIGHT.

04:40.959 --> 04:42.917
AND WE CAN GO BACK THERE,

04:42.959 --> 04:44.917
WE CAN
MAKE THE D.A. CHARGE HIM.

04:44.959 --> 04:47.208
I DON'T KNOW HOW, BUT I WILL
THINK OF SOMETHING.

04:47.250 --> 04:50.000
IT'S ALWAYS DARKEST
BEFORE THE DAWN.

04:54.291 --> 04:56.041
(sighs)

04:56.083 --> 04:59.000
(door closes)

05:00.709 --> 05:04.542
IT'S ALWAYS DARKEST
BEFORE THE DAWN.

05:04.583 --> 05:05.917
(clicks gearshift)

05:05.959 --> 05:09.000
EMILY WENDAL PRESENTED WITH
HYPERTENSION AND EARLY LABOR.

05:09.041 --> 05:10.500
TREATED WITH LABETALOL.

05:10.542 --> 05:12.750
BLOOD PRESSURE STABILIZED.

05:12.792 --> 05:15.041
HER HISTORY INCLUDES
PREECLAMPSIA AND DRUG ADDICTION.

05:15.083 --> 05:17.041
EVERY TEN MONTHS,
RIGHT ON SCHEDULE.

05:17.083 --> 05:19.041
I HEARD EMILY'S BACK.
WHAT, IS SHE FAMOUS?

05:19.083 --> 05:20.709
(sighs)
SHE'S A FREQUENT FLYER.

05:20.750 --> 05:23.041
GETS KNOCKED UP EVERY YEAR
OR SO,

05:23.083 --> 05:25.750
THEN SHOWS UP IN THE E.R.
WHEN SHE'S CLOSE TO TERM.
HEY, I DON'T HAVE
ANY CASH ON ME. DO--

05:25.792 --> 05:27.750
I DO, I DO, I DO. TECHNICALLY,
IT'S MY TURN, RIGHT?

05:27.792 --> 05:29.750
'CAUSE YOU DID THE LAST TWO,

05:29.792 --> 05:32.041
AND CHARLOTTE DID
THE ONE BEFORE THAT.
WH-WH-WHY DO WE NEED CASH?

05:32.083 --> 05:34.959
WE GIVE HER 50 BUCKS,
SHE GIVES UP HER BABY.
WHAT?

05:35.000 --> 05:38.291
IT'S--
WELL, NO, NO, I MEAN, FIRST I
OFFER HER REHAB AND THERAPY.

05:38.333 --> 05:40.417
